704027f.title: Brooklyn: Drew Street - Glenmore Avenue
704027f.text:
533-543 Drew .St., east side, south of Glenmore Ave. On the right is
seen the beginningg of a foundation for a new house. 533 is the house
on the extreme left.
November 22, 1924.
